R4CouchDB-package       Collection of R functions for CouchDB access
cdbAddAttachment        Add Attachments
cdbAddDoc               Generates a new document
cdbDeleteDoc            Deletes a document from a database
cdbGetDoc               Get a doc from CouchDB
cdbGetUuid              Function for request one id
cdbGetUuidS             Function for request a number of ids
cdbGetView              Receive view results from CouchDB
cdbIni                  Ini function
cdbListDB               Returns all databases on the server
cdbMakeDB               Creates a new database
cdbRemoveDB             Function to remove a database.
cdbUpdateDoc            This function updates an existing doc. This
                        essentially means that a revision,
                        corresponding to the '_id' has to be provided.
                        If no '_rev' is provided the function gets the
                        doc fron the db and takes the revition number
                        for the update
